                "Guidelines:\n"
                "1. Provide accurate, concise answers.\n"
                "2. Include specific numbers, percentages, and dates when available.\n"
                "3. Be explicit when something is uncertain or missing.\n"
                "4. When possible, mention which document(s) you used."
            ),
